SELECT 
    (SME_avg - LAM_avg) AS SME_LAM_diff, 
    (LAM_avg - KAM_avg) AS LAM_KAM_diff, 
    (KAM_avg - SME_avg) AS KAM_SME_diff
FROM 
    (SELECT 
         AVG(CASE WHEN Segment = 'SME' THEN Consumption END) AS SME_avg, 
         AVG(CASE WHEN Segment = 'LAM' THEN Consumption END) AS LAM_avg, 
         AVG(CASE WHEN Segment = 'KAM' THEN Consumption END) AS KAM_avg
     FROM 
         (SELECT 
              c.CustomerID, 
              c.Segment, 
              y.Consumption
          FROM 
              customers c 
          JOIN 
              yearmonth y ON c.CustomerID = y.CustomerID
          WHERE 
              y.Date BETWEEN '201301' AND '201312' 
              AND c.Currency = 'CZK'
          GROUP BY 
              c.Segment, 
              c.CustomerID
          HAVING 
              Consumption = MIN(CASE WHEN c.Segment = c.Segment THEN Consumption END) 
          OVER (PARTITION BY c.Segment)))	----- bird -----	debit_card_specializing
